ActCanada Small Business Financing Act
SubjectOrder designating the Minister of Industry as the Minister for the Purposes of the Canada Small Business Financing Act
PrecisOrder (1) Repealing Order in Council P.C. 2023-781 of July 26, 2023; and (2) Designating the Minister of Industry, a member of the King's Privy Council for Canada, as the Minister for the purposes of the CANADA SMALL BUSINESS FINANCING ACT.
